## <a id="1-2-3"></a>v1.2.3

**Release Date:** September 24, 2018

### Features included in this release:


<p class="note breaking"><strong>Breaking Change</strong>: Any automated
  process that updates Pivotal Scheduler might break if the deployment does not
  use a Xenial stemcell.
</p>

The new feature in this release:

* Pivotal Scheduler v1.2.3 and later requires a Xenial stemcell.
  - To download a Xenial stemcell from Pivotal Network,
go to <a href="https://network.pivotal.io/products/stemcells-ubuntu-xenial">
  Stemcells for Pivotal Platform (Ubuntu Xenial)</a>.
  For more information about updating BOSH add-ons and importing the
  stemcell, see <a href="./installing.html">Installing and Configuring Pivotal Scheduler</a>.

### Known Issues

There are no known issues for this release.


